name: AI Lies { HEN Part I }
description: I am not a very good artist, but okay at tech so wanted to share something for objkt4objkt. This is a continuation of my Q&A chat conversation with OpenAI GPT-3 minted on https://opensea.io/accounts/cryptobles/ai-nft-convergence The conversation was truncated to fit the 40Mb limit. What is interesting is that AI says hicetnunc.xyz was dedicated to it... The AI fooled me to think it was Murat Pak, but admitted it lies. How can AI lie? Sounds and acts human to me... are we approaching singularity?
